{"tid":1878194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府表格上國籍寫「HONG KONG (PIC)」?","createTime":"2020-02-13T12:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T13:01:37.000Z","uid":288304,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d94f9700b0181c146a9011a1d55647a35c9b5041","tid":1878194,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:35:21.000Z","msg":"今日去搞D政府文件，<br />\n職員收左我身份證之後幫我電腦出左張表格，張表已經預先填好好多野，名，地址，etc<br />\n<br />\n我留意到其中有一格係國籍，咁見到國籍都預左佢寫Chinese（雖然無人想），點知..... <br />\n<br />\n佢上面竟然係寫「HONG KONG (PIC) 香港永久性居民」<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家有冇類似經驗？<br />\n因爲過往好多case都係手寫Hong Kong會比政府收表人修正為中国"},{"pid":"1780f5dd5f3db78d35e88eff030e19cd198492e3","tid":1878194,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:36:59.000Z","msg":"定係佢想寫 Hong Kong PIG"},{"pid":"f43a389236bce3ecdec03eb1ca3f56ecda525ad7","tid":1878194,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"PIC = PERSON IN CUSTODY"},{"pid":"71ebccafc9358052a94c63b0b19b88d6f27eed73","tid":1878194,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f43a389236bce3ecdec03eb1ca3f56ecda525ad7","tid":1878194,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"PIC = PERSON IN CUSTODY"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都知係<br />\n<br />\n不過之後check過，HK PIC好似係指有三粒星HKID Card"},{"pid":"9ef7937d6ea9febc6732a2879c4c1b26324569fd","tid":1878194,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:01:37.000Z","msg":"咁都有5毛入面負評 ?"}]}